    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-03-24T06:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-03-24T06:00:00-05:00" n="638"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d638">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">751G.00/3–2454: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_DCD1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dillon</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Department of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1954-03-24T12:00:00+01:00"
                            >March 24, 1954—noon.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 10:19 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3500. Repeated information Saigon 398. Last night at dinner with <persName
                        corresp="#p_LJ1">Laniel</persName> he said he was much more encouraged
                    regarding Indochina <pb facs="1184" n="1152" xml:id="pg_1152"/> situation. The
                    action at Dien Bien Phu had, he said, greatly improved morale in France and the
                    spirit of defeatism, which had been rampant only a month ago, was now much more
                    subdued.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_DCD1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Dillon</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
